id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/5525851fecf8130f5d3189de91a9e542" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/picture_18-100x150.jpg" width="67" height="100" alt="Matteo Iemmi" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Matteo Iemmi"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/matteo-iemmi/">View all articles by Matteo Iemmi</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/11/gli-opposti-che-attraggono/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Gli opposti che attraggono</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/11/opera-de-marseilleroberto-devereux-2/" rel="next">Opéra de Marseille:&#8221;Roberto Devereux&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-14847"> <article id="comment-14847" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/89d18d958a4f5f0c173a311d035e1105?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Massimo Rini</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/11/modena-teatro-comunale-romeo-et-juliette/#comment-14847"><time datetime="2011-11-25T15:17:50+00:00">25 novembre 2011 at 15:17</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>L&#8217;ennesimo Romeo. Siamo già al quinto in due anni nel solo nord italia.  Evidentemente vogliamo avvalorare le tesi dei nostri politici, che considerano la lirica come un lusso inutile. Gli stiamo dando ragione. Complimenti.</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2011/11/modena-teatro-comunale-romeo-et-juliette/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sarà pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-requi